dct_title_s: Riparian Conveyances on Delaware River in and near Trenton County of Mercer from records of the former Riparian Commission State of New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Lalor Street to Bridge Street along the Delaware River including Moon Island.
Map shows the grants on the Delaware River such as the grants to the city of Trenton, D.W. Lenox, American Bridge Company, the United New Jersey R.R. and Canal Co., and others.
